                  <choice value="incorrect">The <em>engine control</em> is the <em>control
                              center</em>. The <em>electronic interface</em> is the
                              <em>effector</em>. </choice>
            </multiple_choice>

            <part>
                  <response match="correct" score="1">
                        <feedback><p>Correct. Take a look at the completed
                                    flow<?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20111130T165453-0500" content=" "?>chart
                                    below.</p>
                              <image src="../webcontent/feedback_cruisecontrol.gif"/></feedback>
                  </response>
                  <response match="incorrect" score="0">
                        <feedback><p>Incorrect. Take a look at the completed
                                    flow<?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20111130T165515-0500" content=" "?>chart
                                    below.</p>
                              <image src="../webcontent/feedback_cruisecontrol.gif"/></feedback>
                  </response>
                  <hint>Remember, the receptor senses the variable, in this case the speed.</hint>
                  <hint>Remember, the effector creates a change that will modify the variable, in
                        this case the speed.</hint>
            </part>
      </question>


